OOC: Moo moos? oO;;

BIC:

The overgrown white squirrel darted from tree to tree,
tail streaming out behind her.
'I was aptly nicknamed..' She though wryly, pausing
for a moment to get herself under control.
She panted slightly, and curled her fluffy tail around
her protectively.
SHould she keep running, or go back and fight? She was
almost SURE she'd heard gunfire somewhere in the
distance.
"They better not TOUCH Goldeneye." She said angrily to
herself, her ears flattening in wrath.
Or perhaps it had been Maximals, fighting with the
Preds?
Either way, Tails hoped her very first friend ever
wasn't hurt at all-
"Or else THIS squirrel will exact her revenge..."
Tails muttered, jumping lightly on a broad branch.
